%# While if statements

v = zeros(10,1);
for i=1:10
  v(i) = 2^i;
end;
v

indices = 1:10;
for i=indices,
  disp(i);
end;

i = 1;
while i <= 5,
  v(i) = 100;
  i = i+1;
end;
v

i = 1
while true,
  v(i) = 999;
  i = i+1;
  if i == 6;
    break;
  end;
end;
v

v(1) = 2
if v(1) == 1,
  disp('the value is one');
elseif v(1) == 2,
  disp('the value is two');
else
  disp('the value is not one or two');
end;
